{
  "stem": "7506.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we don't know the place nor the exact date.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother then got married to my stepfather, Charles Nathan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES] No, I wasn't married at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I stopped doing that because my mother was sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my stepfather drove me a bit crazy to get a normal life-- marry a-- find a nice Jewish girl, get married, have a business, all those things.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think it was influential in my decision to leave what I was doing and to try and lead a normal life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I've yet to need a-- I've yet to lead a normal life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got a job as a beautician [PAUSES] in London, although my mother and stepfather lived on the coast of England.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was about an hour's train journey.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to travel up by train every day, six days a week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES] I worked what was then a very nice, good area in London, in a very well-known place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES] And then in 1958, [PAUSES] my uncle came over again from South Africa to visit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a brother in England.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had his father and mother still in England, all family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES] And he paid us a visit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, what do you want to be here for?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, it's cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "England's finished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're too far in Europe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's no good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's dangerous.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It'll never be any good in Europe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why don't you come to South Africa?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES] And I suppose, in a way, I said to myself, why not?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I've always been very geographical in my interests.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I've always traveled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As a child, I was schlepped backwards and forwards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to South Africa.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
